<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Successful - VC</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Oxygen', 'Ubuntu', 'Cantarell', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #000000;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #111111;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .success-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #a1a1aa;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .success-card {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .success-message {
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .reset-details {
            background-color: #111827;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #374151;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #10b981;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #059669;
        }
        
        .button-secondary {
            background-color: #374151;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-left: 12px;
        }
        
        .button-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #4b5563;
        }
        
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .security-tips {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .tip-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #d1d5db;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .tip-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .tip-icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
        }
        
        .warning-box h4 {
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .warning-box p {
            color: #d1d5db;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #333333;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .device-info {
            background-color: #111827;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .device-info .device-label {
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .device-info .device-value {
            color: #d1d5db;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .success-icon {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                font-size: 30px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 4px;
            }
            
            .button {
                display: block;
                margin: 12px 0;
            }
            
            .button-secondary {
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">VC</div>
            <div class="success-icon">‚úÖ</div>
            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 20px; margin: 0;">Password Reset Successful</h1>
            <p style="color: #d1fae5; margin-top: 8px;">Your password has been successfully updated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="title">Password Updated!</h2>
            <p class="subtitle">Your account is now secured with your new password.</p>
            
            <p style="color: #d1d5db; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 16px;">
                Hi <%= name %>,<br><br>
                Great news! Your password for your VC account has been successfully reset and updated. Your account is now secured with your new password.
            </p>
            
            <div class="success-card">
                <div class="success-message">üîí Password Successfully Updated</div>
                <p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
                    Your account is now protected with your new password
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reset-details">
                <h3 style="color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px;">Reset Details:</h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Account Email:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= email %></span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Reset Completed:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= resetTime %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Sign In to Your Account</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h3 style="color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 16px;">üõ°Ô∏è Keep Your Account Secure</h3>
                
                <div class="tip-item">
                    <div class="tip-icon">‚úì</div>
                    <span><strong>Use a strong, unique password</strong> - Combine letters, numbers, and symbols</span>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-item">
                    <div class="tip-icon">‚úì</div>
                    <span><strong>Keep your password private</strong> - Never share it with anyone</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-item">
                    <div class="tip-icon">‚úì</div>
                    <span><strong>Use a password manager</strong> - Store passwords securely</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tip-item">
                    <div class="tip-icon">‚úì</div>
                    <span><strong>Review account activity</strong> - Check for any suspicious logins</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            

            <div style="background-color: #1f2937; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;">
                <h4 style="color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 8px;">üéØ What's Next?</h4>
                <ul style="color: #d1d5db; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Sign in with your new password</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Update your password manager</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Enable two-factor authentication</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 4px;">Review your account security settings</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p class="footer-text">
                This confirmation was sent to <%= email %>. Your password was successfully updated on <%= resetTime %>.
            </p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Security Center</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Account Settings</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Help Center</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">Contact Support</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
